HomeAboutCareers 







Careers

Few people can say they love their job. Fortunately, staff at MEDITECH do. We’re a company that continues to grow even in uncertain economic times, hiring over 4,500 staff members in the last five years.
Our employees make a difference every day whether they’re in product development, client services, marketing, or sales—everyone at MEDITECH contributes to better and safer patient care in hospitals and clinics around the world. But that’s not all, when you work at MEDITECH you’re introduced to a company culture that is becoming more and more rare in the corporate world. You’ll build lasting relationships with your co-workers, receive generous benefits, share in the camaraderie and have fun—all while doing meaningful work.   
If you are seeking a rewarding career with a truly unique company, then take a look at our open positions. Check out our FAQs or contact us with questions, and don’t forget to follow us on Twitter for the latest on @MEDITECHCareers.
Recruitment Fraud Warning
It has come to our attention that various individuals have contacted people offering fake employment opportunities with MEDITECH. Recruitment fraud is a sophisticated scam offering job opportunities to job seekers, typically through bogus websites or through fake emails claiming to be from the company. Such scams are fraudulent and intended to steal money from the victims.
All communication with MEDITECH employees, including our Recruiting team, will come from a meditech.com email address. Any email that does not come from a meditech.com email address should be viewed as suspicious.
MEDITECH will never ask for money transfers, checks, or payments from applicants to secure a position with us. Additionally, all candidates will be expected to come on site for one or more in person interviews before any job offer is made.
For information on protecting yourself and reporting fraud, please feel free to reference some valuable security information that Monster.com has put together on fraud and scams. 




