Medical Information Technology Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 1:47 PM ET
Health Care Technology

Company Overview of Medical Information Technology Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Medical Information Technology, Inc. develops, manufactures, licenses, and supports computer software products for the hospital market. The company offers Electronic Health Record, a cohesive set of software products designed from the outset to work in conjunction with the overall operation of the hospital. It also provides software product to automate the clinical laboratory departments in the hospital, which performs various diagnostic tests on blood or urine specimens; software products for the clinical departments of hospital; hospital billing and accounts receivable, as well as general accounting software; and software for home healthcare, ambulatory, mental health, and long-term care s...
Medical Information Technology, Inc. develops, manufactures, licenses, and supports computer software products for the hospital market. The company offers Electronic Health Record, a cohesive set of software products designed from the outset to work in conjunction with the overall operation of the hospital. It also provides software product to automate the clinical laboratory departments in the hospital, which performs various diagnostic tests on blood or urine specimens; software products for the clinical departments of hospital; hospital billing and accounts receivable, as well as general accounting software; and software for home healthcare, ambulatory, mental health, and long-term care settings. The company markets and sells its products to health care providers primarily in the United States and Canada. Medical Information Technology, Inc. was founded in 1969 and is based in Westwood, Massachusetts.
Detailed Description


MEDITECH CircleWestwood, MA 02090United StatesFounded in 19693,700 Employees



