medical information technology inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Software
Sub-Industry: Application Software
Medical Information Technology, Inc. develops software. The Company manufactures, licenses, and supports computer software products for hospitals, ambulatory care centers, physicians, and home health organizations. Medical Information Technology operates in the State of Massachusetts.




